        "summary": "Blackberry Breakfast Bars requires around <b>45 minutes</b> from start to finish. This dairy free recipe serves 1 and costs <b>$4.23 per serving</b>. This breakfast has <b>2118 calories</b>, <b>23g of protein</b>, and <b>99g of fat</b> per serving. Only a few people made this recipe, and 2 would say it hit the spot. It is brought to you by Foodista. If you have sugar, quick-cooking rolled oats, brown sugar, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. Taking all factors into account, this recipe <b>earns a spoonacular score of 81%</b>, which is spectacular. Similar recipes include <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/blackberry-breakfast-bars-1409135\">Blackberry Breakfast Bars</a>, <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/blackberry-breakfast-cobbler-476553\">Blackberry Breakfast Cobbler</a>, and <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/blackberry-breakfast-cobbler-1760409\">Blackberry Breakfast Cobbler</a>.",
